title: 814. Team Draft Values Based on DJ's Top 150 Prospects
itunes:title: 814. Team Draft Values Based on DJ's Top 150 Prospects
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give storylines for the 5 international games that were announced. Then, the pair discuss team draft values based on DJ's top 150 prospects. To wrap up the show, the duo pick who will win the top positional battles across the league.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
